The QuillBot team seeks to advance that idea by, automating those tasks and allowing their users to focus on what they write, not how they should write it. Whether one is writing emails, social media posts, or essays, QuillBot has their back. It has an arsenal of productivity-enhancing tools that are already changing the way the world writes, and we're looking for world-class talent to change the way people write. Join us if you want to help us lead the way.

Responsibilities:

Design and implementation of the overall web architecture.
Design, construct, and integrate our API offerings.
Contribute to UI/UX improvements to optimize conversions and retention.
Totally understand and contribute to the product road map.
Take complete ownership of features/work and deliver end to end.
Mentor junior developers.